title: Sakthi Leelai
subTitle: Sage Bhringi worships only Lord Shiva, Brahma and Vishnu. When Goddess Parvati stands in his way, he goes to the extent of giving rise to a demon.

title: Kaashmora
subTitle: Kaashmora, a fraudster, gets locked inside a haunted bungalow, along with his clan. Soon, the family faces an army of ghosts who will let them leave only if their wishes are granted.

title: Thaali Kattiya Raasa
subTitle: Mythili falls in love with Pandian, the educated man of her village. However, they have to first deal with Mythili's cruel father who once ruined her sister's life.

title: Diwan
subTitle: A cook falls in love with a wealthy man's daughter. However, after receiving her father's disparaging remarks, he embraces the challenge to amass a fortune within a year.

title: Seevalaperi Pandi
subTitle: Five villagers, unhappy with the judgments of the chief of their village, join forces with his bodyguard Pandi to kill him. But Pandi gets capital punishment while the others are acquitted.

title: Neethana Antha Kuyil
subTitle: A woman vows to seek revenge against those who murdered her husband. Later, she murders Veerababu, an evil landlord, and seeks refuge in a woman's house with her son.

title: Laysa Laysa
subTitle: Chandru's grandfather is going to visit him but Chandru has spent all his money. So he requests his wealthy friend, Rakesh, to pose as the owner of all the riches till his grandfather stays with him.
